---
import Portrait from '../../assets/antoine-bourchardy.png';
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
---

<section class="py-10 sm:py-20 container text-center max-w-[760px]">
    <h2 class="text-h3 sm:text-h2 font-medium intersect-once intersect:animate-slide-in">Why are we open source?</h2>
    <p class="text-quote-sm sm:text-quote text-muted-foreground my-10 sm:my-12 intersect-once intersect:animate-slide-in motion-delay-100">
        “We don't want to push companies to get help on compliance if they don't need to. That's also why we give free advice. We really just want to bring the right support."
    </p>
    <Image
            densities={[1, 2]}
            class="block mx-auto mb-10 sm:mb-12 intersect-once intersect:animate-slide-in motion-delay-150"
            src={Portrait} alt="Portrait of Antoine Bouchardy"
            width={164}
            height={164}
    />
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        — Antoine Bouchardy, Co-founder & CEO
    </p>
</section>
